{"tid":1590010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果唔以武制暴，報警會點？","createTime":"2019-09-23T13:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T13:58:17.000Z","uid":99883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7e02f0b327e919ba0f85bfb240e6a5e708d2446a","tid":1590010,"uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:53:07.000Z","msg":"唔主張使用暴力，但遇到襲擊必定要以適當武力自衛，直到對方投降停止攻擊。報警反而會遇到以下情況：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190923/20773393\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190923%2F20773393&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=7671aa4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190923%2F20773393&h=39155b4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190923/20773393</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】將軍澳居民前晚在PopCorn商場外高唱香港之歌，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一名疑似藍絲中年男子不滿，鬧人後出手打人，引發衝突，多名手持圓盾的防暴警接報到場，卻拘捕兩名分別13歲男童及19歲青年帶署</span></span>，激發居民從四方八面湧來聲討。其間居民批評警方未有舉旗警告下發射兩枚海綿彈，一名男子腹部中槍。至昨凌晨逾百名巿民轉往包圍將軍澳警署，警方首次在區內發射催淚彈驅散，至少七枚催淚彈射上對面民居新都城平台，一名中年居民中槍。有居民慨嘆：「將軍澳終於都有催淚彈！」並直斥警方在民居射催淚彈擾民。"},{"pid":"eefc75b632d404251424beea96f767d36f211d29","tid":1590010,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"444d598cd48333800913bc13424b3459413f1e1e","tid":1590010,"uid":227711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:58:17.000Z","msg":"鶳"}]}